---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="Privacy Policy for True Recall — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
	<div class="legal-page">
		<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="meta">Effective date: March 22, 2026 · Last updated: March 22, 2026</p>

		<p>
			This Privacy Policy explains how True Recall ("<strong>we</strong>", "<strong>us</strong>",
			"<strong>our</strong>") collects, uses, and protects information about you when you use our
			website at <a href="https://truerecall.app">truerecall.app</a> and the True Recall Obsidian
			plugin (collectively, the "<strong>Service</strong>").
		</p>

		<h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
		<p>
			The data controller responsible for your personal data is:<br />
			<strong>Łukasz Piera</strong>, operating under the name True Recall, based in Poland.<br />
			For all data-related enquiries, including GDPR requests, contact us at:
			<a href="mailto:privacy@truerecall.app">privacy@truerecall.app</a>.
		</p>

		<h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
		<p>We collect only what is necessary to provide the Service.</p>

		<h3>Account data</h3>
		<p>
			When you register or log in, we collect your <strong>email address</strong>. We use Supabase
			magic-link authentication — no password is stored.
		</p>

		<h3>Usage data</h3>
		<p>
			We store your AI generation count and subscription tier in our database. This is required to
			enforce plan limits (Free Trial, Pro) and display your usage on the dashboard.
		</p>

		<h3>Payment data</h3>
		<p>
			When paid plans are available, payments will be processed by a third-party payment provider. We do
			<em>not</em> store card numbers or full billing details. We receive only a customer
			identifier, subscription status, and purchase history sufficient to manage your account.
		</p>

		<h3>Analytics data</h3>
		<p>
			We use <strong>Vercel Analytics</strong> to collect anonymous, aggregated page-view
			statistics (pages visited, country, browser type). No cookies are set by True Recall for
			analytics purposes; Vercel Analytics operates without cookies and without collecting personal
			identifiers.
		</p>

		<h3>Data you create in the plugin</h3>
		<p>
			Flashcard content (questions, answers, notes) is stored entirely on your own device inside
			your Obsidian vault. It is <em>not</em> transmitted to our servers unless you explicitly use
			the cloud sync feature.
		</p>

		<h2>3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
		<p>We rely on the following legal bases under GDPR Article 6:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>Contract performance (Art. 6(1)(b))</strong> — processing your email address and
				usage data is necessary to create and manage your account and deliver the Service.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Legitimate interests (Art. 6(1)(f))</strong> — anonymous analytics help us
				understand how the Service is used and improve it. This interest does not override your
				rights.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Legal obligation (Art. 6(1)(c))</strong> — we may process data where required by
				applicable law (e.g. keeping records for tax purposes).
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>4. Third-Party Data Processors</h2>
		<p>
			We share your data only with the processors listed below, each bound by appropriate data
			processing agreements and GDPR-compliant safeguards.
		</p>
		<table>
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>Processor</th>
					<th>Purpose</th>
					<th>Location</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td><a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Supabase</a></td>
					<td>Authentication, database storage</td>
					<td>EU (AWS eu-central-1)</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><a href="https://unkey.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Unkey</a></td>
					<td>API key management & usage tracking</td>
					<td>USA (SCCs apply)</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel</a></td>
					<td>Hosting, anonymous analytics</td>
					<td>USA (SCCs apply)</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Resend</a></td>
					<td>Transactional emails (magic link, waitlist)</td>
					<td>USA (SCCs apply)</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
		<p>
			Where processors are located outside the EU/EEA, transfers are governed by Standard
			Contractual Clauses (SCCs) adopted by the European Commission.
		</p>

		<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
		<p>
			We retain your account data for as long as your account is active. If you request account
			deletion, we will delete your personal data within <strong>30 days</strong>, except where
			retention is required by law (e.g. transaction records for 5 years under Polish accounting
			law). Anonymised or aggregated data may be retained indefinitely.
		</p>

		<h2>6. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
		<p>
			If you are located in the EU/EEA, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Right of access</strong> — obtain a copy of the data we hold about you.</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Right to rectification</strong> — correct inaccurate or incomplete data.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</strong> — request deletion of your
				data, subject to legal retention requirements.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Right to restrict processing</strong> — limit how we use your data in certain
				circumstances.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Right to data portability</strong> — receive your data in a structured,
				machine-readable format.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Right to object</strong> — object to processing based on legitimate interests.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Rights related to automated decision-making</strong> — True Recall does not use
				automated decision-making or profiling.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Right to lodge a complaint</strong> — you may file a complaint with the Polish
				Data Protection Authority (<a
					href="https://uodo.gov.pl"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener">UODO</a
				>) or the supervisory authority in your country of residence.
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@truerecall.app"
				>privacy@truerecall.app</a
			>. We will respond within 30 days.
		</p>

		<h2>7. Cookies</h2>
		<p>
			True Recall does not set tracking or analytics cookies. Supabase sets a session cookie
			strictly necessary for authentication. You cannot opt out of this cookie without losing the
			ability to log in.
		</p>

		<h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
		<p>
			The Service is not directed at children under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect
			personal data from anyone under 16. If you believe a child has provided us with their data,
			contact us and we will delete it promptly.
		</p>

		<h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
		<p>
			We may update this Privacy Policy. For material changes, we will notify you by email (at the
			address associated with your account) at least 14 days before the change takes effect. The
			date at the top of this page always reflects the latest revision.
		</p>

		<h2>10. Contact</h2>
		<p>
			Questions about this policy or your data? Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@truerecall.app"
				>privacy@truerecall.app</a
			>.
		</p>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.legal-page {
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding-top: 2.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.legal-page h1 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
	}

	.meta {
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.legal-page h2 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-top: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);
	}

	.legal-page h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
	}

	.legal-page p,
	.legal-page li {
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
	}

	.legal-page p + p {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	.legal-page ul {
		margin: 0.625rem 0 0.625rem 1.25rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.375rem;
	}

	.legal-page a {
		color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
	}

	table {
		width: 100%;
		border-collapse: collapse;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	th,
	td {
		text-align: left;
		padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
	}

	th {
		background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	td {
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
	}
</style>
